# Tmux / tmux-leader deploy

Whenever you change anything under `roles/tmux/` (including `roles/tmux/leader/` Rust sources and templates), finish by running from the repo root:

```bash
ansible-playbook main.yml --tags tmux
```

Do this in the same session as the code change unless the user explicitly asks to skip deploy. Do not only suggest the command—run it.
